  <title>SET DIGITFIXED Command</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword>Commands</keyword>
    <keyword>Digits<keyword>fixing the number of</keyword></keyword>
    <keyword>Displaying<keyword>numbers</keyword></keyword>
    <keyword>Environment</keyword>
    <keyword>SET DIGITFIXED command</keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">SET DIGITFIXED Command</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><snippet src="__CommandInclude" inline="false"/></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Heading1">Purpose</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">Change the setting that fixes the number of digits used to display numeric output.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Heading1">Syntax</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">SET DIGITFIXED ON | OFF | (&lt;<text styleclass="Italic">lToggle</text>&gt;)</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Heading1">Description</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">SET DIGITFIXED is functionally equivalent to SetDigitFixed(). &#160;</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text"><snippet src="__IncludeLibRT" inline="false"/></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Heading1">See Also</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Function_SetDigitFixed">SetDigitFixed()</link></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
  </body>
</topic>
